---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="The Architecture of Zero-Gravity">
<div class="relative flex min-h-screen w-full flex-col group/design-root overflow-x-hidden">
<div class="layout-container flex h-full grow flex-col">
<!-- Header -->
<header class="flex items-center justify-between whitespace-nowrap border-b border-solid border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 px-10 py-3 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 sticky top-0 z-50">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">
<div class="size-6 text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl">grid_view</span>
</div>
<a href="/" class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight">VibeBlocks</a>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-1 justify-center gap-8">
<div class="flex items-center gap-9">
<a class="text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-400 dark:hover:text-slate-100 text-sm font-medium transition-colors" href="/docs">Docs</a>
<a class="text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-400 dark:hover:text-slate-100 text-sm font-medium transition-colors" href="#">Recipes</a>
<a class="text-primary text-sm font-bold relative pb-1" href="/blog">
                    Blog
                    <span class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-[2px] bg-primary"></span>
                </a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex justify-end">
<button class="flex min-w-[84px] cursor-pointer items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-lg h-9 px-4 bg-primary text-slate-900 text-sm font-bold shadow-sm hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
<span>Deploy</span>
</button>
</div>
</header>

<main class="flex-1 w-full overflow-y-auto">
    <!-- Article Hero -->
    <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-primary via-transparent to-transparent scale-150"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-[1240px] mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-6">
            <span class="bg-primary text-slate-900 text-xs font-black uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Featured</span>
            <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl font-black leading-tight tracking-tight max-w-4xl">The Architecture of Zero-Gravity</h1>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-slate-400 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mt-4">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">person</span>
                    <span>AA Digital Team</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">calendar_today</span>
                    <span>Mar 01, 2026</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">schedule</span>
                    <span>8 min read</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row w-full mt-12 px-6 lg:px-12 pb-24 gap-12">
        <!-- Sidebar TOC -->
        <aside class="hidden md:flex w-1/4 flex-col gap-8 sticky top-32 h-fit">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                <h3 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 px-2">Table of Contents</h3>
                <nav class="flex flex-col gap-1 border-l-2 border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
                    <a href="#introduction" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-primary border-l-2 border-primary -ml-[2px]">Introduction</a>
                    <a href="#core-concepts" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-white transition-colors">Core Concepts</a>
                    <a href="#benchmarking" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-white transition-colors">Benchmarking</a>
                    <a href="#conclusion" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-white transition-colors">Conclusion</a>
                </nav>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 flex flex-col gap-4 overflow-hidden relative">
                <div class="absolute -right-4 -bottom-4 opacity-5 pointer-events-none">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-9xl">rocket_launch</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-bold">Ready to build?</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Experience zero-gravity architecture today.</p>
                <button class="w-full py-3 bg-primary text-slate-900 font-black text-sm rounded-xl shadow-md transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all">Get Started</button>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <!-- Article Content -->
        <article class="flex-1 max-w-[800px] w-full mx-auto md:mx-0">
            <div class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none prose-headings:font-black prose-headings:tracking-tight prose-a:text-primary prose-code:bg-slate-100 dark:prose-code:bg-slate-800 prose-code:rounded prose-code:px-1 prose-code:text-primary prose-blockquote:border-primary prose-blockquote:bg-slate-50 dark:prose-blockquote:bg-slate-900 prose-blockquote:py-2 prose-blockquote:rounded-r-xl">
                <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 font-medium leading-relaxed">
                    VibeBlocks was born out of a single obsession: performance. In this article, we'll dive deep into the zero-gravity architecture that powers the next generation of web frameworks.
                </p>
                
                <h2 id="introduction">Introduction</h2>
                <p>
                    Modern web development has become increasingly heavy. Between hydration mismatches, massive bundles, and complex state management, the "baseline" web experience has grown significantly more resource-intensive over the last decade.
                </p>
                
                <blockquote>
                    "Performance is not a feature; it is the foundation of the user experience." – VibeBlocks Design Philosophy.
                </blockquote>

                <h2 id="core-concepts">Core Concepts</h2>
                <p>
                    The zero-gravity architecture relies on three primary pillars that distinguish it from traditional monolithic frameworks:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Stateless Routing:</strong> Sub-millisecond routing at the edge.</li>
                    <li><strong>Reactive Pruning:</strong> Automatically removing unused logic before delivery.</li>
                    <li><strong>Atomic Hydration:</strong> Only hydrating components that strictly require interactivity.</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Reactive Pruning</h3>
                <p>
                    Unlike traditional tree-shaking, Reactive Pruning analyzes the execution graph and prunes entire dependency trees that are unreachable under static rendering conditions.
                </p>

                <h2 id="benchmarking">Benchmarking</h2>
                <p>
                    In our internal benchmarks, VibeBlocks outperformed traditional frameworks by up to 40% in Time to First Byte (TTFB) and achieved a 60% reduction in client-side bundle size.
                </p>

                <div class="bg-[#0B0E14] rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 my-10 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-3 border-b border-white/10 bg-white/5">
                        <span class="text-slate-400 text-xs font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">benchmarking.vb</span>
                        <div class="flex gap-2">
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-slate-700"></span>
                            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-slate-700"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8 overflow-x-auto">
                        <pre class="font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-300"><span class="text-[#c678dd]">import</span> <span class="text-[#e5c07b]">{</span> <span class="text-[#e06c75]">Bench</span><span class="text-[#e5c07b]">,</span> <span class="text-[#e06c75]">Route</span> <span class="text-[#e5c07b]">}</span> <span class="text-[#c678dd]">from</span> <span class="text-[#98c379]">"@vibeblocks/core"</span><span class="text-[#abb2bf]">;</span>

<span class="text-[#c678dd]">const</span> <span class="text-[#e06c75]">results</span> <span class="text-[#56b6c2]">=</span> <span class="text-[#c678dd]">await</span> <span class="text-[#e06c75]">Bench</span><span class="text-[#abb2bf]">.</span><span class="text-[#61afef]">run</span><span class="text-[#e5c07b]">(</span><span class="text-[#e06c75]">Route</span><span class="text-[#abb2bf]">.</span><span class="text-[#61afef]">main</span><span class="text-[#e5c07b]">)</span><span class="text-[#abb2bf]">;</span>

<span class="text-[#e06c75]">console</span><span class="text-[#abb2bf]">.</span><span class="text-[#61afef]">log</span><span class="text-[#e5c07b]">(</span><span class="text-[#98c379]">"Baseline Latency: "</span> <span class="text-[#56b6c2]">+</span> <span class="text-[#e06c75]">results</span><span class="text-[#abb2bf]">.</span><span class="text-[#e06c75]">latency</span><span class="text-[#e5c07b]">)</span><span class="text-[#abb2bf]">;</span></pre>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h2 id="conclusion">Conclusion</h2>
                <p>
                    The zero-gravity architecture is more than just an optimization; it's a fundamental rethink of how we ship code to the user. By prioritizing the user experience and stripping away the legacy friction of modern frameworks, VibeBlocks sets a new standard for web performance.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Join us in building the zero-gravity web.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-20 pt-10 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 flex flex-col gap-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white">About the Author</h3>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-6 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-primary flex items-center justify-center text-slate-900">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">engineering</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                        <span class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-black">AA Digital Engineering Team</span>
                        <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Pioneering zero-gravity architecture and edge computing solutions for modern web businesses worldwide.</p>
                        <div class="flex gap-4 mt-2">
                            <a href="#" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl text-primary">public</span></a>
                            <a href="#" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl text-primary">share</span></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>
</main>

<footer class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 px-10 py-12 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 text-center">
    <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm font-medium">Engineered by AA Digital Business</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6">
        <a class="text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-400 dark:hover:text-slate-100 text-sm font-medium transition-colors" href="#">GitHub</a>
        <a class="text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-400 dark:hover:text-slate-100 text-sm font-medium transition-colors" href="#">Twitter</a>
        <a class="text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-400 dark:hover:text-slate-100 text-sm font-medium transition-colors" href="#">Discord</a>
    </div>
</footer>
</div>
</div>
</BaseLayout>
